{"tid":1411404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 緊急 成立跨區記者頻道","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T13:33:57.000Z","uid":186,"like":85,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7608c30a91826a6b5764a24b0eb2735c19e451b2","tid":1411404,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:36:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">跨部門記者會<br />\nInter-departmental press conference</div></span></span><br />\n係14年雨革洗腦招式，最終成功令民意轉向<br />\n利用每日重覆海量資訊，令市民無法逐一分析，最終放棄以直覺思考信任政府。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>傳播內容：</strong>將所有嚴重問題強拉落市民到<br />\n例如：波叔講完一大堆無用數字，引起公眾恐慌<br />\n今日波叔講中美貿易戰，一大堆唔明嘅嘢都係想<br />\n以後將恐慌引導到市民到<br />\n<br />\n<strong>傳播方法：</strong>電視，網上，電台，記者<br />\n因為官員講咩，所有媒體都會報到<br />\n<br />\n目標人士：中立，淺及深藍<br />\n<br />\n要打贏跨部門記者會，我地需要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">跨區記者頻道<br />\nInter-district press channel</span></strong></div></span><br />\n<strong>傳播內容：</strong>將所有記者會問題作理性分析，逐一擊破<br />\n將十八區的第一手即時消息，由市民上傳給跟隨者睇到<br />\n<br />\n<strong>傳播方法：</strong>網上，Youtube, Telegram, Instagram, Whatsapp, 製作每日新聞meme 圖作宣傳，airdrop<br />\n<br />\n<strong>目標人士：</strong>十八區香港人，記者<br />\n要贏就要將真實資料畀佢地睇到<br />\n打破同溫層效應"},{"pid":"6be3a8762cf4bc73ab03eb1d8c517ac1a537b75b","tid":1411404,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:37:04.000Z","msg":"需要和理非 作路人記者"},{"pid":"517c3d310ca2901d8d68ab27288ee07a59dc1d53","tid":1411404,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:37:42.000Z","msg":"因為岩岩諗到 岩岩開左tg"},{"pid":"05c2e66ffbe235b7214146664b2a6e2dfebd0785","tid":1411404,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"517c3d310ca2901d8d68ab27288ee07a59dc1d53","tid":1411404,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:37:42.000Z","msg":"因為岩岩諗到 岩岩開左tg"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime