狗個記者會講嘅示威衝突情況<br />\n另外再加番d狗係各區發癲嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n但最大問題係<br />\n我哋個記者會要上到大台<br />\n唔係淨比我哋自己睇<br />\n而係主要做埋比對家睇<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以主動邀請cctvb、東方等紅媒<br />\n雖然我哋真係好唔鐘意佢 甚至想杯葛佢哋<br />\n但敵人主要接觸到示威衝突<br />\n就係呢啲紅媒<br />\n到時只係得番蘋果立場呢d自己友嘅話<br />\n個作用就冇咁大 <br />\n因為大部份內容都係自己友知道<br />\n只係再重覆多一次"},{"pid":"0f340d01003abf3079aca5d2a427b2f533fad679","tid":1411404,"uid":232540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:49:07.000Z","msg":"good idea <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a854a340d28c4fa7d18465386caac0d933a31d9c","tid":1411404,"uid":113124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0061b2022233c60416ac25b9af2c9f7768823081","tid":1411404,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:49:54.000Z","msg":"第一次開 原來group 同 channel 唔同<br />\n<br />\nGroup link: <a href=\"http://t.me/interdistrict18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finterdistrict18&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=deb4fd9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/interdistrict18</a>"},{"pid":"37498f095c4d2f865efd812f56c6f54be7753c80","tid":1411404,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:49:58.000Z","msg":"不要說推<br />\n試著說成立民間記者會"},{"pid":"543835094f0bad4fdc082cffc492435f0238ebc1","tid":1411404,"uid":129243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"由記者安排及主持記者會 點睇 只係反映事實既真相 夠哂公信力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e52899c386fe2c03cb5e1f8d81309d2d9f3179","tid":1411404,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:51:21.000Z","msg":"需要大量路人記者<br />\n唔需要黑衫，只需要手機"},{"pid":"02707b905f6f3f74a5c89d9ca32e76dd70d00ec2","tid":1411404,"uid":142249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201