re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b3b0f9248f4801f4b3249c63b49203652269d7","tid":1411404,"uid":178387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:04:51.000Z","msg":"最好做埋社區播放，就算只係一週大事回顧咁做都好。因為初期未必個個都識上網自己搵，可以視乎是滲透率再決定頻密程度。要課金買物資器材隨便開聲，我第一個支持。"},{"pid":"c08eb3863a7241a85029827c9ad8cac32de2a5c2","tid":1411404,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:07:01.000Z","msg":"有心人士 希望可以加入<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/interdistrict18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finterdistrict18&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=deb4fd9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/interdistrict18</a>"},{"pid":"9c64ef08b1a86d5bf44ff9f0d0d87de85689c0c0","tid":1411404,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:07:13.000Z","msg":"有心人士 希望可以加入<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/interdistrict18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finterdistrict18&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=deb4fd9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/interdistrict18</a>"},{"pid":"5753f7d8f871ea61f42f5ddb726ce0a1fe8f2fbc","tid":1411404,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b16eff5c85dc8861c76fe527c9d6cc06ebb5ca","tid":1411404,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:33:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5e1e9b2b1092cafa6412cd220a359f52e4726962","tid":1411404,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:46:25.000Z","msg":"跨區記者頻道<br />\nTarget: Tvb 政府無報嘅新聞<br />\n訪問受影響市民<br />\n讓市民直接回應跨部門記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/interdistrict18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finterdistrict18&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=1e435b24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/interdistrict18</a><br />\n<br />\n民者記者會<br />\nTarget:搞實體記者會<br />\n有錯請更正<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/civilpresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcivilpresscon&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=c851b236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/civilpresscon</a>"},{"pid":"7d34f5970cf7e5436da3a00dec2680756e1bd279","tid":1411404,"uid":267396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:13:32.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n開記者會或出每日報告，進行文宣及駁政府同黑警歪理！ 繼續善用連儂牆比長輩了解事件！ 加油！"},{"pid":"3fbfef42e1af4e1fa7bf84be9d665b902ad843c6","tid":1411404,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d55648ecae6243705e024baeff085ac1b2683898","tid":1411404,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:32:38.000Z","msg":"各位，之前曾經講過想成立一隊跨區公民記者採訪隊。<br />\n<br />\n公民記者，稱民間記者，是指不屬於傳統傳媒體系以外的新聞工作者，雖然公民記者以「記者」為名，但由於自身或所屬團體大多自外於原本的傳媒產業，且不一定擁有新聞相關的專業素養，因此並不完全能融入於傳媒產業的從業人員當中，例如較不容易取得記者證。<br />\n<br />\n有見近日十八區都有不同的社會動盪，我地想希望收集TVB及政府以外的畫面及聲音。一個記者係無可能跑得禁快去唔同區。為此我地希望招集不同的義務民間記者作第一手的採訪及報導。<br />\n<br />\n目標:<br />\n1. 建立即時的消息。同時，有<strong>系統收集一手資訊</strong>同打官司用途。<br />\n2. 收集市民的聲音作統計分析以打破<strong>同溫層效應（Echo Chamber)</strong>。小弟記我當年雨傘佔路就係輸係抗爭者太沉醉於同溫層。<br />\n3. 以<strong>中立姿態探訪</strong>，讓<strong>小市民</strong>（老人家，小朋友）表達到聲音畀我地做<strong>檢討</strong>同<strong>畀對方壓力</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n我們想盡量用最真實，最表露無遺的事實報道，因為香港人有知情權，每一香港人都可以清楚明白香港現時發生的事情，亦希望大家參與我們的民間記者，令更多香港人知道所有事情的真相。<br />\n<br />\n本表格目標為籌備十八區民間記者採訪隊。<br />\n希望大家可以踴躍參與。<br />\n我地團隊會有專人聯絡你做準備<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/QYrb2k8KDUgwrHUG7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FQYrb2k8KDUgwrHUG7&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=e4084e5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/QYrb2k8KDUgwrHUG7</a>"},{"pid":"26108f901fc5a7ab511d2aa6b1a7d9a2bda4eef7","tid":1411404,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bf8696b4d61855f7f45c5a372c7f46a8f5da69","tid":1411404,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}